                                                            <li style="color: black; text-transform: none;">UPS - You don't need to schedule a separate UPS pickup. Simply atach the label and give to box to any UPS driver when they make their next delivery. You also have the option of dropping off the shipment at your local UPS store or UPS mail services store such as mail boxes etc.</li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
